.TH "vmw_cmdbuf_space_inline" 9 "vmw_cmdbuf_space_inline" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_cmdbuf_space_inline \- Set up a command buffer header with inline command buffer space.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" vmw_cmdbuf_space_inline
.BI "(struct vmw_cmdbuf_man *man "  ","
.BI "struct vmw_cmdbuf_header *header "  ","
.BI "int size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "man" 12
The command buffer manager.
.IP "header" 12
Pointer to the header to set up.
.IP "size" 12
The requested size of the buffer space.
